room_title: Escape room "Alien Blood Bank Robbery" by Can You Rob The Bank? in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: We had a excellent time with our family. Peter was super and so was Storme. Very challenging and fun.

room_title: Escape room "Alien Blood Bank Robbery" by Can You Rob The Bank? in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: Ryan was a great game master. Explained everything well. Loved the alien room. So much to do. Very interactive and creative puzzles. Looking forward to do another room.
